Accounting Studies Across the World

The list below allows you to filter for any country (source) in which you are interested.Papers are included if they mention the respective country, and variations thereof (e.g. ‘Denmark’ and ‘Danish’), in the title, abstract, or keywords in research papers published in a list of accounting journals since 1993. For the selection of journals and more details of the search process underlying this information, please refer to the paper. If further questions remain, please contact the authors. We would like to ask that you cite this paper if you use this resource. The list of papers will be updated once a year. Note that we do not cover studies in the U.S.A. due to the large number of papers on this country.

Last update: April 8, 2024 (papers published by the end of 2023)
